title 0.6 Spa New Note


note over Browser
On pressing the save button, the form information 
is handled via the .js file, the code in the .js 
file creates a note from the form, adds it to the 
note list, regenerates the note list on the screen 
without the need to reload the page and finally 
sends the new note to the server.
end note

Browser->Server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
Server-->Browser: {"message":"note created"}
